quran[20{c,v,t}:
15,32,( khuda ne farmaya ) ke iblees! tujhekiya howa ke to sajda karne walon mein shaamil nah howa
15,33,( is ne ) kaha ke mein aisa nahi hon ke ensaan ko jis ko to ne khankhnate srhe hue gaaray se banaya hai sajda karoon
15,34,( khuda ne ) farmaya yahan se nikal ja. to mardood hai
15,35,aur tujh par qayamat ke din taq laanat ( barsay gi )
15,36,( is ne ) kaha ke perwar-digaar mujhe is din taq mohlat day jab log ( marnay ke baad ) zindah kiye jayen ge
15,37,farmaya ke tujhe mohlat di jati hai
15,38,waqt muqarrar ( yani qayamat ) ke din taq
15,39,( is ne ) kaha ke perwar-digaar jaissa tunay mujhe raste se allagkiya hai mein bhi zameen mein logon ke liye ( gunaaho ) ko aaraasta kar dukhao ga aur sab ko behkaon ga
15,40,haan un mein jo tairay mukhlis bande hain ( un par qaboo chalna mushkil hai )
15,41,( khuda ne ) farmaya ke mujh taq ( pounchanay ka ) yahi seedha rasta hai
15,42,jo mere ( mukhlis ) bande hain un par tujhe kuch qudrat nahi ( ke un ko gunah mein daal sakay ) haan bad raahon mein se jo tairay peechay chal parre
15,43,aur un sab ke waday ki jagah jahannum hai
15,44,is ke saat darwazay hain. har aik darwazay ke liye un mein se jamaten taqseem kar di gayi hain
15,45,jo mut-taqi hain woh baghoon aur chashmo mein hon ge
15,46,( un se kaha jaye ga ke ) un mein salamti ( aur khatir jama se ) daakhil hojao
15,47,aur un ke dilon mein jo kudorat hogi un ko hum nikaal kar ( saaf kar ) den ge ( goya ) bhai bhai takhton par aik dosray ke samnay baithy hue hain
15,48,nah un ko wahan koi takleef puhanche gi aur nah wahan se nikalay jayen ge
15,49,( ae paighambar ) mere bundon ko btado ke mein bara bakhsnay wala ( aur ) meharban hon
15,50,aur yeh ke mera azaab bhi dard dainay wala azaab hai
15,51,aur un ko ibrahim ke mehmanon ka ahwaal suna do
